gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 124, Cavaliers 121
gameRecap.excerpt: The Raptors defeated the Cavaliers, 124-121. Pascal Siakam led the way for the Raptors with 36 points, five rebounds, and five 3PM, while RJ Barrett (19 points, nine rebounds) and Immanuel Quickley (14 points, six rebounds, two 3PM) added a combined 33 points for the Raptors in their debut. Caris LeVert tallied 31 points (12-20 FG), four rebounds, and four assists for the Cavaliers in the losing effort. The Raptors improve to 13-20 on the season, while the Cavaliers fall to 18-15.
